==Russian==
[[Category:Russian adjectives]]
[[Category:ru:Food and drink]]
===Adjective===
'''чернушный''', чернушная, чернушное, чернушные (černúšnyj, černúšnaja, černúšnoje, černúšnyje) ''m/f/n/pl''

# having a rich, dark [[complexion]], dark-brown eyes and black hair ''(usually said of girls or women)''.
# of or pertaining to the [[black cumin]] herb or flower ''(Nigella sativa)'', also called [[Roman coriander]], [[black caraway]], [[black seed]], [[nutmeg flower]] or [[love in the mist]].

